long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use the spacebar to make the green ball jump. Jump over the rockets being fired at you. 

The ball rolls faster and the speed of the rockets increase while you play, and your real speed is calculated and show in pixels per second. Your high score is automatically saved to your local storage.
